casebody.data:
No. 10-6170. Tyrone Leslie Farris, Petitioner v. Oklahoma. 562 U.S. 998, 131 S. Ct. 522,

178 L. Ed. 2d 366,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8414. November 1, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Oklahoma dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
